OL,6,FWrexham Council has said it does not
OL,7,Fexpect "wholesale changes" to after
OL,8,Fthe conceded last month there will be
OL,9,F"adjustments" to the policy.
OL,11,FIn a statement the council said any
OL,12,Falterations in the area "will be of a
OL,13,Ftargeted nature."
OL,15,FThe controversial policy, which has
OL,16,Fseen numerous protests take place
OL,17,Fafter the default speed limit on Welsh
OL,18,Froads was reduced to 20mph, was
OL,19,Fintroduced in September last year.
